	<span style="font-size:14px;">The essential guide for all those interested in going for an extended bike trip.  It will cover planning, equipment selection, preparing for a first tour and the lifestyle on the road.  Touring is a fun, awesome way to travel, but requires extensive planning to avoid the many possible pitfalls that come with a long time on the road.  Make your trip great by starting it with this class!</span></p>
