	<span style="font-size:14px;">One of our most popular classes is a three-part in-depth workshop to teach you proper techniques for truing and building wheels.  Students will learn the ins and outs of spoke length calculation</span><span style="font-size:14px;"> along with how to properly lace, tension, dish and true wheels </span><span style="font-size:14px;">.  You are welcome to use recycled wheels/components from the Bike Depot or order new parts and leave the class with a new hand-built wheelset!  </span></p>
