	<span style="font-size:14px;">This class unlocks the mysteries of your all those pesky cables on your bike.  We will walk you through the cable systems for brakes and derailleurs, show you the basics of installation, and cover the adjustments and factors that contribute to crisp, clean shifting and braking.  Another great class to dip your toe into the world of Bike Maintenance.</span></p>
